g.text: Visualizations are divided into two eras of dance
Each era is introduced with a featured dance’s radials These are isolated by body part
Then you will see a set of three dances represententing the eraThese radials show all movements made by all parts of the dancer’s body
At the end of each era’s section, you’ll see an overview ofall three dancesFinally, at the end of this piece you’ll see an overview of all sixdances along with their measure indices and radialsEnjoy.
